🔐 Key Features

  • 👤 Face Registration: Use your webcam to register new faces by name. Faces are stored with precise timestamps in a secure database.
  • 🎥 Live Face Recognition: Watch real-time webcam streams as the system detects and identifies multiple known faces with bounding boxes and name labels.
  • 💬 AI Q&A Assistant: Ask natural questions like:
    • “Who was the last person registered?”
    • “When was John added?”
    • “How many faces are stored?”
    Powered by a Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) engine using ChatGPT and vector search.

This platform combines React, Flask (Python), and AI for an interactive, browser-based facial recognition experience.
